197f0e644bf402ee9cf1c621a0daf3426659ca05610aa7b6d8bed3d81f1d1c77c0a81ef35a92fa42b271c7f814d718ec1d1b61f5f4b554b3735142903b70e32b  fix-getproto.patch"
